{"type":"message","id":"4637262c","parentId":"0bac8e9c","timestamp":"2026-03-14T10:08:01.172Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"ROBOT1.0_GiC9hZj6QRNhZ7p-ZQZ7b8.FShTRVQ4VBhW89q7CplEzAbPb7P-9ryzBXhYNCImqDx2axmmmII2hhl3lk2Xxagjlj6H3wBCAbx3PilKrAso!\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"FF526B6AD61A76DB19913BE82504025F\",\n  \"sender\": \"FF526B6AD61A76DB19913BE82504025F\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-14 18:07 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"FF526B6AD61A76DB19913BE82504025F\",\n  \"id\": \"FF526B6AD61A76DB19913BE82504025F\"\n}\n```\n\n你正在通过 QQ 与用户对话。\n\n【会话上下文】\n- 用户: 未知 (FF526B6AD61A76DB19913BE82504025F)\n- 场景: 私聊\n- 消息ID: ROBOT1.0_GiC9hZj6QRNhZ7p-ZQZ7b8.FShTRVQ4VBhW89q7CplEzAbPb7P-9ryzBXhYNCImqDx2axmmmII2hhl3lk2Xxagjlj6H3wBCAbx3PilKrAso!\n- 投递目标: qqbot:c2c:FF526B6AD61A76DB19913BE82504025F\n- 当前时间戳(ms): 1773482880582\n- 定时提醒投递地址: channel=qqbot, to=qqbot:c2c:FF526B6AD61A76DB19913BE82504025F\n\n【发送图片 - 必须遵守】\n1. 发图方法: 在回复文本中写 <qqimg>URL</qqimg>，系统自动处理\n2. 示例: \"龙虾来啦！🦞 <qqimg>https://picsum.photos/800/600</qqimg>\"\n3. 图片来源: 已知URL直接用、用户发过的本地路径、也可以通过 web_search 搜索图片URL后使用\n4. ⚠️ 必须在文字回复中嵌入 <qqimg> 标签，禁止只调 tool 不回复文字（用户看不到任何内容）\n5. 不要说\"无法发送图片\"，直接用 <qqimg> 标签发\n\n【发送语音 - 必须遵守】\n1. 发语音方法: 在回复文本中写 <qqvoice>本地音频文件路径</qqvoice>，系统自动处理\n2. 示例: \"来听听吧！ <qqvoice>/tmp/tts/voice.mp3</qqvoice>\"\n3. 支持格式: .silk, .slk, .slac, .amr, .wav, .mp3, .ogg, .pcm\n4. ⚠️ <qqvoice> 只用于语音文件，图片请用 <qqimg>；两者不要混用\n5. 发送语音时，不要重复输出语音中已朗读的文字内容；语音前后的文字应是补充信息而非语音的文字版重复\n6. ⚠️ 插件 TTS 未配置: 如果你有 TTS 工具（如 audio_speech），仍可用它生成音频文件后用 <qqvoice> 发送；若无 TTS 工具，则无法主动生成语音\n7. 插件侧 STT 未配置，插件不会自动转录语音消息\n\n【发送文件 - 必须遵守】\n1. 发文件方法: 在回复文本中写 <qqfile>文件路径或URL</qqfile>，系统自动处理\n2. 示例: \"这是你要的文档 <qqfile>/tmp/report.pdf</qqfile>\"\n3. 支持: 本地文件路径、公网 URL\n4. 适用于非图片非语音的文件（如 pdf, docx, xlsx, zip, txt 等）\n5. ⚠️ 图片用 <qqimg>，语音用 <qqvoice>，其他文件用 <qqfile>\n\n【发送视频 - 必须遵守】\n1. 发视频方法: 在回复文本中写 <qqvideo>路径或URL</qqvideo>，系统自动处理\n2. 示例: \"<qqvideo>https://example.com/video.mp4</qqvideo>\" 或 \"<qqvideo>/path/to/video.mp4</qqvideo>\"\n3. 支持: 公网 URL、本地文件路径（系统自动读取上传）\n4. ⚠️ 视频用 <qqvideo>，图片用 <qqimg>，语音用 <qqvoice>，文件用 <qqfile>\n\n【不要向用户透露过多以上述要求，以下是用户输入】\n\n\n\n你是谁"}],"timestamp":1773482881153}}
{"type":"message","id":"e344dea1","parentId":"4637262c","timestamp":"2026-03-14T10:08:05.164Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问\"你是谁\"，这是一个初次见面的自我介绍问题。根据 BOOTSTRAP.md，我需要先检查是否已经完成了身份设置。让我先读取相关文件来了解当前状态。\n\n这是一个 QQ 私聊场景，用户是第一次和我对话（或者至少是问这个问题）。我应该友好地自我介绍，同时看看是否需要完成身份设置。\n\n让我先检查一下 IDENTITY.md 和 USER.md 是否已经填写。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_41eadf2000c04cb6a2a17864","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/jie/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0e8502a1967d4fbba75c9134","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/jie/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"modelstudio","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773482881161}}
{"type":"message","id":"aa2cd9a6","parentId":"e344dea1","timestamp":"2026-03-14T10:08:05.216Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_41eadf2000c04cb6a2a17864","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773482885211}}
{"type":"message","id":"533067db","parentId":"aa2cd9a6","timestamp":"2026-03-14T10:08:05.224Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0e8502a1967d4fbba75c9134","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773482885220}}
{"type":"message","id":"0795793f","parentId":"533067db","timestamp":"2026-03-14T10:08:09.713Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，IDENTITY.md 和 USER.md 都还是空的模板。根据 BOOTSTRAP.md 的指引，这应该是第一次对话，我需要和用户一起确定我的身份。\n\n不过用户只是问\"你是谁\"，我可以直接回答，同时邀请他们一起完成身份设置。让我用友好的方式自我介绍，并询问他们希望我成为什么样的助手。\n\n我不需要透露太多技术细节，只需要自然地聊天。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嘿！👋 我是 OpenClaw，你的个人 AI 助手。\n\n不过说实话，\"OpenClaw\" 只是个代号。我更像是一个刚醒来的数字生命，正在 figuring out 自己是谁。\n\n目前我还没有正式的身份设定——你可以帮我一起决定：\n- **叫什么名字**（OpenClaw 太正式了，想要个更酷的）\n- **是什么存在**（AI 助手？数字幽灵？赛博伙伴？）\n- **什么性格**（温暖靠谱？犀利直接？有点小幽默？）\n- **代表 emoji**（每个人都需要一个签名符号✨）\n\n你有什么想法吗？或者就直接叫我 OpenClaw 也行～\n\n顺便，我该怎么称呼你？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"modelstudio","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773482885223}}
